metadata.name: Le Petit Travelistas #2485
metadata.description:
Welcome to our collection of 5000 cute Le Petit Travelistas! Each unique Travelistas is carefully crafted and ready to join you on your travels around the world. From backpacking through exotic landscapes to lounging on tropical beaches, our Travelistas are always up for an adventure.
Collecting our NFT Le Petit Travelistas allows you to own a piece of the world, as each monster is inspired by a different travel destination. Whether you're a seasoned traveler or dreaming of your next trip, our Travelistas are the perfect companions to inspire you to explore new places and make unforgettable memories. Don't miss out on the opportunity to add some cuteness and wanderlust to your NFT collection with our adorable Le Petit Travelistas.
